data.description: This lovely 4-bedroom, 2.5 bath home needs some TLC but has great potential. Large, corner lot centrally located in the established Wells Place subdivision. This spacious home with mature landscaping offers all formals with separate den and eat-in nook off of the kitchen. All bedrooms are located upstairs. The master bathroom features his and hers closets, and the master bathroom has an updated walk-in shower.
